{
  "stem": "13623.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember much, but if I remember the adults talking to us whatever happened in Germany and with Hitler and so on was so remote that it-- the adults were talking about it, but it didn't mean much to us.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know much about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it really didn't mean much to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940, we were occupied by Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hungary was an ally at the time of Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] The part of northern Transylvania that I lived in was occupied by Hungarian army, and things started to change slowly in the town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The remaining-- we had what they called Gendarme.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of-- there were police, but they called them Gendarme, or the Hungarians called them [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Part of their uniform was that they had feathers, and they had like feathers in their hat, like rooster feathers type.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was part of their uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As things got-- as things went on and we got into more of anti-Semitism, we had a nickname for them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We call them the feathers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Instead of saying the police are coming, we said the feathers are coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And after they occupied us we-- for a short while thereafter, I still went to the same public school, to the same cheder.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The difference was that public school was compulsory to change from Romanian that we grew up with that language into Hungarian language.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Slowly, things started to change.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Before where men of military age would, would be drafted into the army, now men of military age were drafted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If they were non-Jewish, they went into the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Jewish boys that were drafted went into a labor battalion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't wear any kind of uniform, but they had to wear a yellow armband.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
